{"tid":2062226,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"老老豆豆 612其實有咩意義？","createTime":"2020-06-13T04:01:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-13T14:55:08.000Z","uid":347987,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"da2e9ed0fc375683b941a5b5287da48d4a06d53e","tid":2062226,"uid":347987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T04:01:55.000Z","msg":"#我們的故事 【6.12不賣慘 欲和平先備戰】<br />\n<br />\n尼采：「殺不死我的，使我更強大。」（Was mich nicht umbringt, macht mich stärker.） 去年6月12日，眾志成城，漏夜渡江，和勇不分，一心只為「撤回」。 拋頭髗曬熱血的戰鬥場面，使共同體中的我們既痛心卻又更團結。但6.12在今天的意義不應是「賣慘式的情緒勒索」，身為政治領袖應當探討6.12的教訓，為民族未來更多的「6.12」而準備。<br />\n<br />\n6.12最大教訓是政權教導了群眾一個道理-「槍桿子出政權」。當民眾和平的聲音被政權充耳不聞，極權採用制度上的暴力去無視民意，強行立法。政權在6.12用催淚彈，橡膠子彈，布袋彈去驅散香港人。由當刻起，港共政權的道理就是「槍械，火藥，子彈」。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">若果想迫使野蠻政權屈服於民意，重返文明的談判桌；香港人首先要學習他們的道理，以武裝力量合法自衛。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n6.12另一個教訓是群眾應因時制宜，拋棄舊有觀念。當民眾被洗腦式以「愛與和平」去感化敵人，跪求敵人給予憐憫，臨陣放下屠刀。可是，早在2014年「讓愛與和平佔領中環」已證明此路不同。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但一眾所謂政治領袖，依然叫大家相信舊有的口號， 愚惑大眾。強行持堅舊有的公式，也只是把一具僵屍強行復活。</span></span>香港人面對歷史的洪流，口號也要與時並進，「 本土抗暴，唯一出路」。 「汝欲和平，必先備戰」（Si vis pacem, para bellum），<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">6.12的教訓便是沒有備戰而奢望和平的來臨。</span></span>我者應與時間競賽，為下場戰役積極備戰。<br />\n<br />\n#本土抗暴 #唯一出路 #養兵千日 #用在一朝 <br />\n<br />\n＿＿＿＿＿＿＿<br />\n#劉澤鋒 -Instagram&bull; Nathanlau612<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/nathanlau612?igshid=69lzavz7f9o3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fnathanlau612%3Figshid%3D69lzavz7f9o3&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJroD442Ur5281Gkz3GsmHlD8%3D&h=9cccc434\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/nathanlau612?igshid=69lzavz7f9o3</a><br />\n-Facebook &bull; 劉澤鋒 Nathan Lau<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/Nathanlau612/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2FNathanlau612%2F&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJroD442Ur5281Gkz3GsmHlD8%3D&h=d86a1c6d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/Nathanlau612/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8iGoTnb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8iGoTnb.jpg&h=7510d9af&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"efaefbb7400ef2829c698098363e740e76f0f5c4","tid":2062226,"uid":347987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T04:03:25.000Z","msg":"義無反顧陳淑莊"},{"pid":"c03063a0dc469cc7e27b202cfbcfcdf4e5113a3b","tid":2062226,"uid":347987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T04:29:10.000Z","msg":"OMDB <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09e10b33cc7f76921cc71d7966d61d28dee5df0a","tid":2062226,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T07:54:53.000Z","msg":"If you want peace, go prepare for war<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f1bade086bf635a7852e4d1cd89d5512f26e399","tid":2062226,"uid":347987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09e10b33cc7f76921cc71d7966d61d28dee5df0a","tid":2062226,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T07:54:53.000Z","msg":"If you want peace, go prepare for war<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T14:55:08.000Z","msg":"We lose a battle<br />\nBut we will win the war<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}